      <li>Securing or removing items of high value before service</li>
      <li>Ensuring pets are secured or appropriately managed during cleaning</li>
      <li>Providing access to water and electricity as needed for cleaning tasks</li>
      <li>Communicating any special requirements or concerns prior to service</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  
  <section class="mb-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Cancellation Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-3">Cancellations must be made at least 24 hours prior to the scheduled service time to avoid cancellation fees. Cancellations made less than 24 hours before the scheduled service may be subject to a cancellation fee equal to 50% of the estimated service cost.</p>
