    <p class="mb-3">WellKnown Cleaning reserves the right, at its sole discretion, to modify or replace these Terms at any time. If a revision is material, we will provide at least 30 days' notice prior to any new terms taking effect.</p>
    <p>By continuing to access or use our services after any revisions become effective, you agree to be bound by the updated terms. If you do not agree to the new terms, please stop using the services.</p>
  </section>
  
  <section class="mb-6">
